{"tid":1553021,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最正英詞//《願榮光歸香港》Glory be to thee, Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T17:11:19.000Z","uid":33269,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"93bf252f5cd88c56c1408f6433efd28bcc6aaa37","tid":1553021,"uid":33269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"七劍浣春秋巴打嘅英詞喺我見到最鍾意嘅版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家傳揚開去！<br />\n<br />\n原post here 👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》英文歌詞 &quot;Glory be to Thee, Hong Kong&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547782\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547782</a><br />\n<br />\n//<strong>《願榮光歸香港》</strong><br />\n曲: thomas dgx yhl<br />\n詞（中文）: t, 眾連登仔 (唔知佢地想唔想咁寫)<br />\n詞（英文）: 七劍浣春秋<br />\n<br />\n中文歌詞好正～<br />\n有英文版可能會更容易 sell 畀外媒～～～<br />\n小試牛刀  不喜勿插～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />PPPPPPPPP<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《願榮光歸香港》  </strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">As we yearn, our freedom nighs</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With eyes blinded, long it comes the night</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight</span><br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!</span><br />\n捍自由   <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We shall strike</span><br />\n來齊集這裡  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">This perilous night</span><br />\n來全力抗對  <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">With hope, with song, with dignity!</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!</span>//"},{"pid":"ebbeb175cb2280195394b774a52424517e86243d","tid":1553021,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"推 依版真係最正"},{"pid":"5b8f24cb0e643a5de265566072d6ed74ac0d3b5f","tid":1553021,"uid":288821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"核能推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c161560a888198e875dbc3fa75fad62ed4b